Package com.rb.nonbiz.types

Class AcceptableFrequency

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.types.AcceptableFrequency
public class AcceptableFrequency
extends java.lang.Object
A Range of UnitFractions.

Represents that something must happen e.g.

  • between 80% of 90% of the time
  • always
  • never
  • more than 70% of the time
  • ... etc
See Also:
UnitFraction
